The paper discusses indoor scene understanding for autonomous agents, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) techniques. The use of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) is also mentioned. Additionally, the paper involves a survey of existing literature, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and graphics (cs.GR).
